#People-to-people Messaging Interface Prototype

## Overview
A visual concept for a mobile messaging interface, focusing on user profile design and message list structure. This design exploration could serve as a foundation for a citizen-engangement communication tool.

## Status
*Ul exploration (Work in Progress)

## Design Features
- **Profile Card Design:** Visualizing user identity and social links.
- **Message List Structure:** Creating a clean, readable layout for communication histories.

## Tool
- Figma

